' === Include / Extend relationships ===
UC_Capture ..> UC_Extract : <<include>>
UC_Capture ..> UC_CheckDomain : <<include>>
UC_CheckDomain ..> UC_SendLogs : <<include>>
UC_SyncWL ..> UC_ApplyFW : <<include>>
UC_EnableWL ..> UC_SaveSnap : <<include>>
UC_SendLogs ..> UC_ReceiveLogs : <<include>>
UC_Heartbeat ..> UC_SyncWL : <<extend>>\n(if version mismatch)
UC_Login ..> UC_RefreshJWT : <<extend>>

' === RBAC notes ===
note right of Agent
  Agent is an automated Windows
  client. Uses API Key for
  /agents/register, then JWT
  (with auto-refresh + revocation)
  for /agents/heartbeat,
  /whitelist/agent-sync, /logs.
end note

note left of Teacher
  Teacher role has ownership-based
  RBAC: can only operate on groups
  in their teacher_ids list and the
  agents / logs / whitelist entries
  belonging to those groups
  (see RBACService).
end note

note bottom of UC_SetPolicy
  Modes: whitelist_only | isolate |
  reset | custom_whitelist | none.
  Stored in agent_policies collection.
end note

@enduml
